author: Today
title: Fans fete Star Wars on China’s Great Wall
text: China&India Fans fete Star Wars on China’s Great Wall A fan dressed as a character from "Star Wars" poses for a photo in front of five hundred replicas of the iconic Storm Troopers at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS A fan dressed as a character from "Star Wars" poses for a photo in front of five hundred replicas of the iconic Storm Troopers at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS A fan holding a helmet of the Storm Trooper character from "Star Wars" poses for a group photo next to a cat at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS A fan dressed as a character from "Star Wars" poses for a photo in front of five hundred replicas of the iconic Storm Troopers at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS Five hundred replicas of the iconic Storm Trooper characters from "Star Wars" are seen on the steps at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS Fans holding toy lightsabers arrive at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS Chinese Star Wars fans hold lightsabers as they pose for a photo at the Juyongguan section of the Great Wall of China during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS A Chinese Star Wars fan playfully swings a lightsaber at a person dressed as a Wookie during a promotional event for "Star Wars - The Force Awakens" on the outskirts of Beijing, China. Photo: REUTERS
